Multiple URI/URL per resource (1)

  • Long discussion on list, key issues were:

    • Can a WebDAV resource have more than one URI?
    • Can a WebDAV collection resource have more than one URI?
      • Resolution: yes, any WebDAV resource can have more than one URI.
    • Are terms URI/URL used consistently?
      • Resolution: some inconsistent use was fixed in -10, some may linger. Needs review.
